And I cooked it and made
the best meal she's ever had.

25:22.667 --> 25:24.300
I got a standing ovation
that night.

25:24.300 --> 25:26.400
These two can go.
- The pressure's on.

25:26.400 --> 25:28.433
- This is the fun part.

25:28.433 --> 25:30.266
- Oh, thank you very much.

25:30.266 --> 25:32.133
- That's with no chicken.
