25:35.533 --> 25:36.700
in a Thai broth.

25:36.700 --> 25:38.000
Some of you have chicken.

25:38.000 --> 25:39.300
Some of you have
just vegetables.

25:39.300 --> 25:40.567
Some of you have brown rice.

25:40.567 --> 25:43.300
Bon appétit, enjoy.
all: Thank you.

25:43.300 --> 25:45.333
- Goodness, the flavor.
- So good.

25:45.333 --> 25:46.700
- This is delicious.

25:46.700 --> 25:48.200
- And this is only
meal number one.

25:48.200 --> 25:49.200
- [laughing]

25:49.200 --> 25:50.300
- They said it's amazing.

25:50.300 --> 25:51.333
They love it.
They--

25:51.333 --> 25:52.734
- Yay!

25:52.734 --> 25:55.433
- It's the first meal,
and no blow-ups.

25:55.433 --> 25:57.300
No fighting.
So I'm hoping it's a sign

25:57.300 --> 25:59.734
of things to come,
and there's not a dark side

25:59.734 --> 26:01.467
to my little chilled-out chef.

26:01.467 --> 26:03.066
- Okay, let's figure out
these yoga mats, guys.

26:03.066 --> 26:04.333
We need to get these in.

26:04.333 --> 26:06.066
