29:56.633 --> 29:58.400
[laughter]

29:58.400 --> 29:59.533
- You banged her.

29:59.533 --> 30:01.066
[laughing]

30:01.066 --> 30:03.200
♪ ♪

30:03.200 --> 30:05.400
- How--where are we at?
